\c 22
\s Rwiyo rwaDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakataura kuna Jehovha mashoko erwiyo urwu nezuva Jehovha raakamusunungura paruoko rwevavengi vake vose nemuruoko rwaSauro\x + Eki. 15.1. Vato. 5.1. Map. 18. 1 Makor. 16.7.\x*.
\v 2 Ndokuti\x + Map. 18.2-50.\x*: Jehovha idombo rangu\x + Map. 31.3. 71.3.\x*, nenhare yangu, nemununuri wangu kwandiri\x + Map. 91.2. 144.2.\x*,
\v 3 Mwari wedombo rangu\x + 22.32,47. Det. 32.4.\x*, ndichatizira kwaari\x + VaHeb. 2.13.\x*; chidzitiro changu\x + 22.31. Gen.. 15.1.\x*, nerunyanga rweruponeso rwangu\x + Ruk. 1.69.\x*, shongwe yangu yakakwirira\x + Map. 9.9. 46.7,11. 59.9,16,17. 62.2, 6.\x*, neutiziro hwangu\x + Map. 59.16. Jer. 16.19.\x*. Muponesi wangu, makandiponesa pakumanikidzwa.
\v 4 Ndichadana kuna Jehovha, wakafanira kurumbidzwa\x + 1 Makor. 16.25. Map. 48.1. 96.4.\x*; naizvozvo ndichaponeswa kubva kuvavengi vangu.
\p
\v 5 Nokuti mafungu erufu akandikomba, mafashame ezvakaipa akandivhundusa.
\v 6 Mabote eSheori akandikomberedza, misungo yerufu yaiva mberi kwangu.
\v 7 Pakutambudzika kwangu ndakadana kuna Jehovha, uye ndakadana kuna Mwari wangu\x + Map. 120.1. Jona 2.2.\x*; iye ndokunzwa inzwi rangu ari mutembere yake, uye kuchema kwangu kwakava munzeve dzake\x + Map. 18.6.\x*.
\v 8 Ipapo nyika yakadengenyeka ndokudedera\x + Vato. 5.4.\x*; nheyo dzekumatenga dzakadengenyeka, ndokuzununguka, nokuti iye waiva atsamwa\x + Job. 26.11.\x*.
\v 9 Kwakakwira utsi kubva mumhino dzake, uye moto wakaparadza kubva mumuromo make; mazimbe akapfutidzwa nawo.
\v 10 Wakakotamisawo matenga, ndokuburuka\x + Map. 144.5. Isa. 64.1.\x*; nerima gobvu raiva pasi petsoka dzake\x + Eki. 20.21.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino wakatasva kerubhi ndokubhururuka; akaonekwawo ari pamapapiro emhepo\x + Map. 104.3.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino wakamisa rima kuva dumba mativi ake ose\x + Job. 36.29.\x*, muunganidzwa wemvura, makore makobvu emuchadenga.
\v 13 Mukupenya pamberi pake kwakapfuta mazimbe emoto.
\v 14 Jehovha wakatinhira ari kumatenga\x + 1 Sam. 2.10. 7.10. Job. 37.4. Map. 29.3. Isa. 30.30.\x*, uye Wekumusoro-soro wakabudisa inzwi rake.
\v 15 Zvino wakatuma miseve\x + Det. 32.23. Map. 7.13. 77.17. 144.6. Habh. 3.11.\x*, ndokuvaparadza; mheni, ndokuvavhiringidza\x + Josh. 10.10.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino migero yegungwa yakaonekwa, nheyo dzenyika dzakaratidzwa pachena, pakutsiura kwaJehovha\x + Map. 106.9. Nah. 1.4. Eki. 15.8.\x*, pakudhuuka kwemweya wemhino dzake.
\p
\v 17 Wakatuma ari kumusoro, akanditora\x + Map. 144.7.\x*, akandinyukura kubva mumvura zhinji\x + Eki. 2.10.\x*.
\v 18 Wakandinunura kubva pamuvengi wangu wakasimba, kune vanondivenga; nokuti vane simba kundipfuura\x + 22.1.\x*.
\v 19 Vaiva mberi kwangu nezuva renjodzi yangu, asi Jehovha wakava mutsigiri wangu\x + 22.6.\x*.
\v 20 Wakandibudisirawo kunzvimbo yakafara\x + Map. 31.8. 118.5.\x*, akandinunura, nokuti waifadzwa neni\x + 15.26.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Jehovha wakandipa mubairo zvichienderana nekururama kwangu\x + 22.25. 1 Sam. 26.23. 1 Madz. 8.32. Map. 7.8.\x*; wakanditsivira zvichienderana nekuchena kwemaoko angu\x + Map. 24.4.\x*.
\v 22 Nokuti ndakachengeta nzira dzaJehovha\x + Gen.. 18.19. Zvir. 8.32.\x*, uye handina kubva kuna Mwari wangu nekuipa.
\v 23 Nokuti mitongo yake yose yaiva pamberi pangu\x + Map. 119.30,102.\x*; nezvimiso zvake handina kutsauka pazviri.
\v 24 Ndaivawo ndakarurama pamberi pake\x + Gen.. 17.1.\x*, uye ndakazvichengeta kubva pane chakaipa changu.
\v 25 Naizvozvo Jehovha wakanditsivira zvichienderana nekururama kwangu\x + 22.21.\x*, zvichienderana nekuchena kwangu pamberi pemeso ake.
\p
\v 26 Kune ane tsitsi munozviratidza mune tsitsi; kumurume wakarurama munozviratidza makarurama\x + Mat. 5.7.\x*.
\v 27 Kune wakachena munozviratidza muri wakachena; uye kune wakatsauka munozviratidza makatsauka.
\v 28 Nevanhu vanorwadziswa muchaponesa\x + Eki. 3.7.\x*; asi meso enyu ari pamusoro pevanozvikudza, mucha\add va\add*deredza.
\v 29 Nokuti muri mwenje wangu, Jehovha; Jehovha achavhenekera rima rangu.
\v 30 Nokuti nemwi ndakamhanya \add nepakati\add* pehondo; naMwari wangu ndakauruka rusvingo.
\p
\v 31 Mwari, nzira yake yakakwana; shoko raJehovha rakaidzwa\x + Map. 12.6. 119.140. Zvir. 30.5.\x*; ndiye nhovo kune vose vanotsvaka uvando kwaari\x + 22.3. Map. 17.7.\x*.
\v 32 Nokuti ndiani Mwari kunze kwaJehovha? Uye ndiani dombo kunze kwaMwari wedu\x + 1 Sam. 2.2. Isa. 45.5,6. Det. 32.31,39. Map. 86.8.\x*?
\v 33 Mwari inhare yangu \add ne\add*simba\x + Map. 27.1. 28.8. 31.4.\x*; uye anokwanisa nzira yangu\x + Job. 22.3. Map. 101.2,6. 119.1.\x*.
\v 34 Unoita tsoka dzangu se\add dze\add*nondokadzi\x + 2.18. Habh. 3.19.\x*, uye anondimisa pakakwirira pangu\x + Det. 32.13. 33.29. Isa. 58.14.\x*.
\v 35 Anodzidzisira maoko angu hondo, zvekuti uta hwendarira hunovhunwa nezvanza zvangu\x + Map. 144.1.\x*.
\v 36 Makandipawo chidzitiro cheruponeso rwenyu, uye unyoro hwenyu hwakandikurisa.
\v 37 Makafarikanyisa nhanho yangu pasi pangu; kuti tsoka dzangu dzisatedzemuka\x + Zvir. 4.12.\x*.
\p
\v 38 Ndakadzingirira vavengi vangu ndokuvaparadza, uye handina kudzoka kusvika vapedzwa.
\v 39 Zvino ndakavapedza, ndokuvabaya, zvekuti havamuki; asi vakawa pasi petsoka dzangu.
\v 40 Nokuti makandisunga chiuno nesimba kuitira hondo\x + Map. 18.32,39.\x*; makakotamisira pasi pangu vakandimukira\x + 22.49. Map. 44.5.\x*.
\v 41 Makandipawo mutsipa wevavengi vangu, kuti ndiparadze vanondivenga\x + Gen.. 49.8. Eki. 23.27. Josh. 10.24.\x*.
\v 42 Vakatarira, asi paiva pasina muponesi; kuna Jehovha, asi haana kuvapindura\x + Job. 27.9. Zvir. 1.28. Isa. 1.15.\x*.
\v 43 Zvino ndakavakuya\x + Eki. 30.36. Job. 14.19.\x* seguruva renyika\x + 2 Madz. 13.7.\x*; ndakavatswa sedope renzira dzemumusha\x + Mik. 7.10. Zek. 10.5. Isa. 10.6.\x*, ndikavaparadzira\x + Gen.. 1.6. Map. 18.42.\x*.
\p
\v 44 Uye makandinunura pakukakavadzana kwevanhu vangu\x + 19.9,43. 20.1,2,22.\x*; makandichengeta ndiri mukuru wendudzi\x + 8.1-14.\x*; vanhu vandaiva ndisingazivi vakandishandira\x + Isa. 55.5.\x*.
\v 45 Vatorwa vachazviwisira pasi pangu; pakunzwa kwenzeve, vachateerera kwandiri.
\v 46 Vatorwa vachasvava, vagobuda munhare dzavo\x + Mik. 7.17.\x* vachidedera\x + Map. 76.10.\x*.
\v 47 Jehovha mupenyu; uye ngarikudzwe dombo rangu; ngaakwiridzirwe Mwari, dombo reruponeso rwangu\x + Map. 95.1. Det. 32.15. Map. 89.26. Map. 18.46.\x*.
\v 48 NdiMwari anonditsivira zvakazara, uye anoderedza marudzi pasi pangu\x + Map. 144.2.\x*.
\v 49 Uye anondibudisa kubva pavavengi vangu, nepamusoro pevanondimukira makandisimudzira\x + 22.40. Map. 59.1.\x*; uye pamunhu wekumanikidza kwazvo makandinunura\x + Map. 140.1.\x*.
\v 50 Naizvozvo ndichakurumbidzai Jehovha, pakati pendudzi, uye ndichaimbira zita renyu rumbidzo\x + VaRom. 15.9. Map. 18.49.\x*.
\v 51 Anokurisa ruponeso rwamambo wake\x + Map. 144.10.\x*; unoitira muzodzwa wake unyoro\x + Map. 89.20.\x*, kuna Dhavhidhi nekumbeu yake nekusingaperi\x + 7.12,13,29. Map. 89.29.\x*.